Title: Work Order: Kirin Tor Offensive I
Description:
<Yoon keeps the details of this order short, but detailed.>

Another request has come through for the Alliance. The Kirin Tor Offensive, located out on the Isle of Thunder, has requested a bushel of juicycrunch carrots.

Though this Horde and Alliance conflict still gets my fur in a bristle, I won't turn away a hungry stomach.
ObjectivesText: Plant 8 Juicycrunch Carrot Seeds on Sunsong Ranch.
